metadata.title: Giantex Kitchen Cart with Storage, Small Kitchen Island on Wheels w/Drawer, 3 Hooks, Rolling Trolley w/Wood Butcher Countertop, Door Cabinet, Serving Utility Cart for Dining Room, White
features: [Classified Storage Space]: Our practical kitchen island features 1 wide countertop, 1 sliding out drawer, 1 open shelf, 3 side hooks and 1 door cabinet to fulfill your daily storage needs. You can sort out your cups, wines, vegetables, fruits, spice jars and tableware in different storage space to keep your room tidy and clean.

[Rubber Wood Countertop]: The wear-resistant rubber wood countertop offers you a perfect place to prepare food and access to what you need. The countertop can bear a weight up to 80 lbs. Selected rubber wood material ensures high durability. Besides, smooth and waterproof surface allows for easy cleaning.

[Flexible Universal Wheels with Lock]: This kitchen cart is equipped with 4 flexible swiveling casters, including 2 lockable wheels, which ensures smooth moving and firm fixation. Different from other wheels, our PP wheels are designed with upgraded metal connector and brakes, which is durable and not easy to crack.

[More Considerate Design]: Exquisite handles of drawer and door bring you much convenience when you want to take out items. Magnetic catch, premium hinge and metal drawer slide ensure effortless opening or closing. Apart from that, faux wood grain top makes the whole kitchen island even more attractive.

[Compact Size & Easy Assembly]: Compared with other large kitchen island, our compact serving cart measures 22” x 18” x 35” (L x W x H), which saves space. In addition, thanks to its simple structure and clear user manual, our kitchen island can be easily and quickly assembled, which saves your time and energy.
description: Description: Our small kitchen island cart is a perfect storage solution for narrow spaces. It has 1 sliding out drawer under the top, 1 open shelf in the middle and 1 door cabinet on the bottom, allowing you to better organize different stuff. And the casters with metal brakes is not easy to crack. To offer more convenience, we also design it with convenient handles, magnetic catch and premium hinge. In addition, the kitchen serving cart is easy to assemble with clear instruction and complete accessories. Features: 1 sliding out deep drawer, 1 open shelf, 3 handy hooks and 1 door cabinet for storage Wide enough countertop for food preparation High-quality as well as selected rubber wood material for high durability Smooth and waterproof surface for easy cleaning 2 swiveling casters and 2 lockable casters ensure easy moving Upgraded wheels with metal connector are superior to other plastic wheels Easy-to-grip handle for quick access Magnetic catch and premium hinge for convenient use Simple structure and detailed user manual for easy installation Perfect for kitchen, dining room, living room, etc Specifications: Color: White Material: Rubber Wood, MDF, Engineer Wood, PP, PVC Overall Dimension:22"x 18"x 35" (L x W x H) Drawer Size: 15.5" x 13.5" x 3" (L x W x H) Door Size: 17"x 10.5"(L x W) Cabinet Size: 18"x 16"x 12" (L x W x H) Open Shelf Size: 17.5"x 16"x 10.5"(L x W x H) Clearance from Ground: 5" Load Capacity of the Top: 80 lbs Load Capacity of the Drawer: 11 lbs Load Capacity of Open Shelf: 30 lbs Load Capacity of Door Cabinet: 30 lbs Load Capacity of Each Hook: 10 lbs Net Weight: 32 lbs Package includes: 1 x Small Kitchen Island Cart 1 x Instruction
